{"tid":1470172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日人民日報及微信瘋傳，琴晚個陷阱應一應","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T04:46:37.000Z","uid":251121,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1073b83fc08923b5b65b32f74e05dbaaee12b8b9","tid":1470172,"uid":251121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JCsfW3T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJCsfW3T.jpg&h=b0daf7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SV5M3JU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSV5M3JU.jpg&h=e353eace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vwi3mvA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVwi3mvA.jpg&h=0b14c247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴晚班差佬入左去又出番黎，同時間呢條友浮上水面，重唔係收到風陷阱啟動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222f074dc95f8538f92a77ac926adf38b87530ed","tid":1470172,"uid":149630,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:30:02.000Z","msg":"陳雲：<br />\n做錯事不道歉，是違反道德的啊。這個當然，但我們不是在小學課室，由班長和班主任裁判，我們是在戰場上，警察、法官、電視台、報紙、觀眾都是中共的人。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你道歉，對方就有材料展開政治謠言宣傳，而且要求你再為其他你無做過的事道歉（例如毆打北京記者），之後你拒絕，他們就向你開火射擊。</span></span>做錯了事就馬上走，不是道歉！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">普選勝利了，在民選元首認為安全的情況</span></span>，才為以往的錯失道歉，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">道歉也是元首來做，不是民眾來做</span></span>，賠償也是用政府的錢，不是民間眾籌。"},{"pid":"d876d1fb4a4a03de63e1899c5b3319afdde6b1fd","tid":1470172,"uid":60594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:30:34.000Z","msg":"收皮"},{"pid":"50b3bb47db79900102e85d272cf323155def84ac","tid":1470172,"uid":195540,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:31:13.000Z","msg":"幾時連中國既民意都係行動既考慮因素<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90815371b601937ac1cd6f2fb4ac2efe34c547e3","tid":1470172,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:31:28.000Z","msg":"根本係做戲啦<br />\n由鳩班支那種叫"},{"pid":"c77f959c82f3023b1687d0bcbcfc68d92d59ac64","tid":1470172,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:32:01.000Z","msg":"人民日報有腦嘅大陸人自己都唔睇啦 同北韓飛機文有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cae02f419b1c70c0c010964e2ff52c51ee240720","tid":1470172,"uid":60594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:33:33.000Z","msg":"唔洗理中計撚"},{"pid":"77b34559e5f0a79e3ef527cce755f98d15921e2e","tid":1470172,"uid":57665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:42:13.000Z","msg":"香港事務純屬香港內政 由不得支那勢力說三道四"},{"pid":"1ab007f3efcaf1840d2284a9db48b5d97e37ea2a","tid":1470172,"uid":140022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:46:37.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂 外媒唔係咁講咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}